{"navVariant":"base","head":{"title":"Buying your Freehold  | Moonstone Advocates","description":"Buying the freehold of a leasehold property can give you greater control, long-term security and clarity over costs. Whether you own a leasehold flat or leasehold house, there are legal routes available to help you secure the freehold. As members of the Association of Leasehold Enfranchisement Practitioners and The Property Institute, we have recognised experience and practical knowledge to support you through the process with confidence.","ogTitle":"Buying your Freehold  | Moonstone Advocates","ogDescription":"Buying the freehold of a leasehold property can give you greater control, long-term security and clarity over costs. Whether you own a leasehold flat or leasehold house, there are legal routes available to help you secure the freehold. As members of the Association of Leasehold Enfranchisement Practitioners and The Property Institute, we have recognised experience and practical knowledge to support you through the process with confidence.","ogType":"website","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","canonical":"buying-your-freehold.html","jsonLd":["{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Buying your Freehold \",\n  \"description\": \"Buying the freehold of a leasehold property can give you greater control, long-term security and clarity over costs. Whether you own a leasehold flat or leasehold house, there are legal routes available to help you secure the freehold. As members of the Association of Leasehold Enfranchisement Practitioners and The Property Institute, we have recognised experience and practical knowledge to support you through the process with confidence.\",\n  \"url\": \"/for-businesses/business-leasehold-enfranchisement-management/buying-your-freehold\",\n  \"inLanguage\": \"en\",\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-07-10T15:39:29.470Z\",\n  \"dateModified\": \"2026-07-10T15:39:29.470Z\",\n  \"about\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Service\",\n    \"name\": \"Buying your Freehold \",\n    \"description\": \"Buying the freehold of a leasehold property can give you greater control, long-term security and clarity over costs. Whether you own a leasehold flat or leasehold house, there are legal routes available to help you secure the freehold. As members of the Association of Leasehold Enfranchisement Practitioners and The Property Institute, we have recognised experience and practical knowledge to support you through the process with confidence.\",\n    \"provider\": {\n      \"@type\": \"LegalService\",\n      \"name\": \"Moonstone Advocates\"\n    },\n    \"serviceType\": \"Leasehold Enfranchisement & Management\",\n    \"url\": \"/for-businesses/business-leasehold-enfranchisement-management/buying-your-freehold\"\n  },\n  \"mainEntity\": {\n    \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\n    \"mainEntity\": [\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Can I buy the freehold of my individual flat?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"No. You have join with the other flat owners to purchase the freehold of the whole building jointly. \"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Will I have a freehold flat once we buy the freehold?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"No. Your individual flat will still have a separate leasehold title, and if you have a mortgage your lender’s charge will be registered on your leasehold title. \"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Why do I need to extend my lease, if we own the freehold?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Because your flat is still held under a separate leasehold title, and the lease will continue to reduce in length if you don’t extend the lease. \"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"What do we do if the landlord is missing?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"You can apply to the court to buy your freehold. \"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}"]},"blocks":[{"tag":"main","attrs":{"className":"main-wrapper"},"html":"<header data-wf--02-standard-header--variant=\"dark\" data-wf-component-id=\"949280b8-8e72-c6a2-5bfc-7cfb2eeda9b8\" data-wf-variant-state=\"8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\" class=\"section_header w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div class=\"padding-global is-page-top\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"simple_header_grid\"><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf8719e-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h1 class=\"heading-style-h1\">Buying your Freehold </h1></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Buying the freehold of a leasehold property can give you greater control, long-term security and clarity over costs. Whether you own a leasehold flat or leasehold house, there are legal routes available to help you secure the freehold. As members of the Association of Leasehold Enfranchisement Practitioners and The Property Institute, we have recognised experience and practical knowledge to support you through the process with confidence.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-btn-hover=\"\" data-theme=\"primary\" href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn is-icon w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Speak to an expert</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf871aa-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-right\"><div class=\"simple-header_image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">Home</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/for-businesses\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">For businesses</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Buying your Freehold </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_shape-wrapper w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div lottie=\"target-load\" class=\"header_shape is-standard\" data-w-id=\"5d828c84-1f1c-1e38-bfb3-80ffb8d04940\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69db9824cf9ff19dd03c1c29_08fdbca2c62ae345f765f433c8401fe4_Blacks_V_Blue.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"1\" data-is-ix2-target=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"0\" data-loading=\"lazy\"></div></div><div class=\"simple-header_background-image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer\"></div><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_background-image\"></div></header><section class=\"section_benefit-grid_layout\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid benefit-grid_list\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Collective enfranchisement allows flat leaseholders to buy the freehold together</h4><p>Leaseholders can join forces to purchase the freehold of their building. This statutory right gives you greater control over management, costs, and long-term decisions affecting your property.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>The building must meet specific legal criteria to qualify</h4><p>The building must be self-contained, or part of a self-contained building. No more than 25% of the building is non-residential. At least two flats must be owned by qualifying tenants with leases longer than 21 years.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>At least half of qualifying tenants must take part in the purchase</h4><p>A minimum of 50% of qualifying leaseholders must participate in the collective purchase. Working together strengthens your position and allows the process to move forward.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>A professional valuation confirms the premium payable to the freeholder</h4><p>You will need a specialist enfranchisement valuation before serving notice. This confirms the premium payable and ensures the statutory notice includes an accurate figure.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Leaseholders have the right of first refusal if the landlord plans to sell</h4><p>If the landlord decides to sell the freehold, qualifying leaseholders must be given the opportunity to buy first under Section 5 of the Landlord and Tenant Act 1987.</p><p>‍</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Qualifying tenants must respond to the Section 5 notice within two months</h4><p>More than 50% of qualifying tenants must accept the Section 5 offer together within two months of the notice being served.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>The price in a Section 5 offer is set by the landlord</h4><p>You accept the price and terms stated in the Section 5 notice. The legislation does not allow negotiation once the offer is made.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Leaseholders of houses can buy the freehold through agreement with the landlord</h4><p>Houses are treated differently to flats. You can negotiate directly with the landlord to agree terms for the freehold purchase. This approach can be more flexible where both parties are willing to engage.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>The law provides a statutory route where agreement cannot be reached</h4><p>If terms cannot be agreed, you can apply to purchase the freehold of your leasehold house under the Leasehold Reform Act 1967. The legislation sets out the process and valuation approach.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_accordion\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"faq6_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_content\"><div class=\"faq6_content-left\"><h2>Questions we’re often asked</h2><div class=\"margin-top margin-small\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button is-secondary w-button\">Speak to an expert</a></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_list\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_list-grid\"><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f7d\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Can I buy the freehold of my individual flat?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>No. You have join with the other flat owners to purchase the freehold of the whole building jointly. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f88\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Will I have a freehold flat once we buy the freehold?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>No. Your individual flat will still have a separate leasehold title, and if you have a mortgage your lender’s charge will be registered on your leasehold title. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f93\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Why do I need to extend my lease, if we own the freehold?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Because your flat is still held under a separate leasehold title, and the lease will continue to reduce in length if you don’t extend the lease. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f9e\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>What do we do if the landlord is missing?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>You can apply to the court to buy your freehold. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Thank you Anushka and all your team for looking after us so well and protecting our interests. It’s made potentially stressful situations straightforward. Very much appreciated.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Leasehold Enfranchisement Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Black Solicitors LLP. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using blacks, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I would have no hesitation in recommending Anushka and the Leasehold team to anyone seeking specialist leasehold advice and assistance.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Leasehold Enfranchisement Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Anushka and her colleagues were always professional, approachable and responsive, making what can often be a complex and time-consuming process feel straightforward and well managed. Their dedication to achieving positive outcomes for their clients was evident throughout.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Leasehold Enfranchisement Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The team demonstrated great knowledge and expertise throughout the process. As we were managing multiple lease extensions simultaneously, their organisation, efficiency and attention to detail were invaluable.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Leasehold Enfranchisement Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I have had the pleasure of working with Anushka and the Leasehold Team on several lease extension matters, and I highly recommend them - fantastic team! </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Leasehold Enfranchisement Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the UK</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone Advocates and Julie Powell in particular was a huge help with one of our client&#x27;s lease extension processes. She handled everything smoothly and kept communication clear and consistent throughout. Her proactive approach really made things easier for everyone involved. Great to work with and I look forward to working with her in the future.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Leasehold Enfranchisement Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_team\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"slider-main_component\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Experts in every area</h2><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div hover-zoom=\"trigger\" class=\"team-member_item\"><a href=\"/our-people/josh-ackroyd\" class=\"team-member_item w-inline-block\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"team-member_image-wrapper\"><img hover-zoom=\"target\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b44ab164a8844c96471e18/6a1ef97a44382dc9d8ff702c_6953d8f0080093a3775b624c_BLACKS-JMA-PHOTOGRAPHY-DSC_7053%2520-low-res.jpeg\" class=\"image is-team\"></div></div><div class=\"team-member_text-wrapper\"><div fs-list-field=\"full-name\" class=\"text-size-large text-weight-semibold\">Josh Ackroyd</div><div class=\"hidden-text\"><div fs-list-field=\"first-name\">Josh</div><div fs-list-field=\"last-name\" class=\"text-size-large text-weight-semibold\">Ackroyd</div></div><div class=\"article-meta\"><div fs-list-field=\"job-title\" class=\"secondary_tag\">Paralegal</div></div></div></a></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"